items.text:
It takes almost an hour, but you finally get Dace’s group to the safety
of the far bank of the Silverfin River. Dace herself carries the last of
the people—a young boy—in a bounding flight across the water.
Accompanied by a rush of wind, she gracefully lands beside you.
“Thank you,” she says. “I can take it from here.”
on the campaign tracker, and return Dace, Ambitious Shaper to the collection.
